	<p class="bodyTitle">
		Medicaid and CHIP in The United States Virgin Islands (USVI)
	</p>
	<div class="blueBox">
		<p class="bodyText">Medicaid which includes the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP) provides health and long-term care coverage to some people with limited income, including children and parents, pregnant women, people with disabilities, and seniors. In the Virgin Islands, the Medicaid Program is also known as MAP or Medical Assistance. The program is designed to ensure access to quality medical care.</p> 
	</div>
